	(gr_text_box "PCB:\n\n* Product Type: Industrial/Consumer electronics\n* Different Design: 1\n* Delivery Format: Single PCB\n* PCB Thickness: 1.6 mm\n* PCB Colour: Black\n* Silkscreen: White\n* Material Type: FR4-Standard TG 135-140\n* Surface Finish: ENIG\n* Gold Thickness: 2 U{dblquote}\n* Outer Copper Weight: 1 oz\n* Inner Copper Weight: 1 oz\n* Specify Layer Sequence: No\n* Impedance Control: Yes\n* Layer Stackup: JLC061611-7628\n* Via Covering: Epoxy Filled & Capped\n* Min Via Hole Size/Diameter: 0.15mm/(0.25/0.3mm)\n* Board Outline Tolerance: ±0.2mm(Regular)\n* Confirm Production File: Yes\n* Mark on PCB: 2D barcode (Serial Number)\n	* Printing: Number Only\n	* Prefix:\n	* Unique Number: Keep\n	* Starting Value: 0001\n	* 2D Barcode Position: Specify Position\n* Gold Fingers: No\n* Castellated Holes: No\n* Press-Fit Hole: No\n* Edge Plating: No"
